<h2>Permissions Required</h2>

<p>
    Each FAQ had three permissions which determine who can change what in
    that particular question.
</p>

<dl>
    <dt>admin</dt>
    <dd>
        allows you to change the attributes of the <strong>FAQ</strong>
        itself
    </dd>

    <dt>view</dt>
    <dd>
        allows you to see the list of <strong>questions</strong> in the admin
        interface
    </dd>

    <dt>edit</dt>
    <dd>
        allows you to add/edit and delete <strong>questions</strong> from this
        <strong>FAQ</strong>
    </dd>
</dl>

